name: Moon Flower I
description: I have always been obsessed with the different lunar phases and with their magical meanings. Flowers have also been an integral part of my life as an artist, due to their different colours and beauty. In this piece I wanted to combine my love for flowers and the moon. I chose the colour blue for this first one, as I feel my soul is connected to this colour.  Size: 10984 x 2953px, 300dpi
